01:22:31.710 --> 01:22:32.750
Son...

846
01:22:33.460 --> 01:22:35.460
Put it in, hurry.

847
01:22:39.340 --> 01:22:40.670
That's right. Hurry.

848
01:22:51.550 --> 01:22:53.920
Once more.

849
01:22:55.960 --> 01:22:57.380
Over there.

850
