the spirits bother my salat
to send a message

862
01:24:23.840 --> 01:24:25.880
because sometimes I'm not focused.

863
01:24:26.590 --> 01:24:29.880
We need to believe
that we live side by side

864
01:24:29.960 --> 01:24:32.130
