891
01:26:38.960 --> 01:26:41.170
She always want to grow deeper in religion

892
01:26:43.420 --> 01:26:44.750
to be a Quran memorizer.

893
01:26:50.550 --> 01:26:51.800
Her name is Ningsih.

894
01:26:53.210 --> 01:26:54.500
